The paper also involves combinatorial optimization and graph theory, which could place it in the discrete mathematics (cs.DM) or graph theory (cs.GT) sub-categories. Finally, the mention of linear time algorithms suggests that it could also belong to the algorithms and data structures (cs.SI) sub-category.
